actions.message:
Hello there! Need help? Here are all the commands below me!
**Current prefix: !**

**General Commands**
``userinfo``,``serverinfo``,``ping``,``poll``,``ytsearch``

**Fun Commands**
``guess``, ``kys``,``pixelate``,``screen``

**Music Commands**
``play``, ``skip``, ``volume``, ``stop``

**Imaging Commands**
``pixelate``, ``kys``,``screen``

**Moderator Commands** (Staff Only)
``kick``,``ban``, ``mute``, ``say``, ``purge``

**For more information about commands, run ``!<commandname>``**
Example: !pixelate
